Refer to the Microsoft Azure Experiment screenshot:

1. Click into experiments on the left side and open a blank page. 
2. Click into saved datasets and upload the recommender lab package that is in this folder as well as the Sales Data set that is in this repository
3. Drag the icons exactly the way it is show on the screen shots
4. Click on "Execute R Script" icon and copy the Microsft Azure R code into the box
5. Click Run and wait for it to finish
6. Click Deploy as web service
7. Click onto web services and you will see the API key shown in the second screen shot
